text: Cabal Online is a free massive multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) created by ESTsoft Corporation. == Characters == There are eight characters players can choose from in Cabal Online. They are: Warrior, Blader, Magician, Force Archer, Force Blader, Force Shielder, Force Gunner, and Gladiator.
